{"tid":2257411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩岸角力｜捷克軍火商向台推銷 72小時後即收大陸警告","createTime":"2020-10-25T06:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T06:45:49.000Z","uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7be0af16d647486c2f1ac8105cc95faafc669823","tid":2257411,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"台灣《上報》報道，捷克軍火商Excalibur Army早前向台灣推銷武器，惟簡報後72小時，軍火公司總部接到來自中國駐捷克大使館的電話，警告不得賣任何裝備給台灣。軍火公司驚訝消息怎會這麼快洩露至中共。台灣中科院表示，簡報內容均為公開資資、不屬機密敏感事項，至於中方作為，因不屬查證權責範圍，中科院不評論。<br />\n<br />\n完整版自己禁link 睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201024/O45PAY4QCNCWXPEY7HMOF3ZFBA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2U2dcjmxH_hjfo8woK14X-KNLslMBVL_CiIamVPmKdGlc6YMLKHSGoZhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201024%2FO45PAY4QCNCWXPEY7HMOF3ZFBA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2U2dcjmxH_hjfo8woK14X-KNLslMBVL_CiIamVPmKdGlc6YMLKHSGoZhA&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=b1430ee7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201024%2FO45PAY4QCNCWXPEY7HMOF3ZFBA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2U2dcjmxH_hjfo8woK14X-KNLslMBVL_CiIamVPmKdGlc6YMLKHSGoZhA&h=a712229d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201024/O45PAY4QCNCWXPEY7HMOF3ZFBA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2U2dcjmxH_hjfo8woK14X-KNLslMBVL_CiIamVPmKdGlc6YMLKHSGoZhA</a>"}]}